1. *Igraj* sa mnom fudbal (Play football with me).
2. *Igrajući* se sa decom, vreme je brzo prošlo (Playing with the children, time passed quickly).
3. Ona voli da *igra* karte (She likes to play cards).
4. Naši učenici su se *igrali* na terenu (Our students were playing in the field).
5. *Igrajmo* u parku (Let's play in the park).